message: Hello! Welcome to Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I'm happy to chat with you today. I have a question about my policy.
That's great to hear! I'm here to help. Before proceeding, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Sure, my full name is Rebecca Thompson.
Thank you for completing security, Rebecca. How can I assist you with your policy today?
I recently had some damage to my car and need to make a claim. How can I go about doing that?
I'm sorry to hear about the damage to your car. A possible resolution could be to initiate the claim process by providing some details. Could you please confirm your date of birth for verification?
Of course, my date of birth is 15/07/1990.
Thank you for confirming, Rebecca. Let's proceed with the claim process. Can you provide me with the first line of your address and postcode?
My address is 123 Sunny Lane, Postcode AB12 3CD.
Great, thank you for that information. I have run through security successfully. To proceed with your claim, we may need some additional details. Could you please confirm your email address?
Sure, my email address is rebeccathompson@email.com.
Thank you for completing security, Rebecca. I'll start the process to help with your claim. Please allow me a moment to review your policy.
Thank you so much, Chris. I really appreciate your help.
You're welcome, Rebecca. I understand this may be a difficult time for you. I'm glad that I was able to help. Is there anything else I can assist you with?
No, that's all sorted for now. Thank you for your assistance, Chris.
You are welcome, Rebecca. If you need further help in the future, please don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day!
